Directed by Park Seon-ho.

Written by Seol Hee Han. Bo-Hee Hong. Hae Hwa.

Cast  Se-Jeong Kim( Shin Ha Ri 1) . Seol In-ah( Jin Young Seo 1) . Min-Kyu Kim( Cha Sung Hoon 1) . Byungchan( Shin Ha Min 1) . Seo Hye-won( Jo Yoo Jung 1) . Jung Young-joo( Han Mi Mo 1) . Lee Deok-hwa( Kang Da Goo 1) . Lim Ki-Hong( Gye Bin 1) . Kim Kwang-gyu( Shin Joong Hae 1) . Won-Seok Song( Lee Min Woo 1) . Yoon Sang-Jeong( Kim Hye Ji 1) . Lee Ki-young( Chairman Jin ) . Han Ji-Hyo( Da Hye ) . Kim Jeong-yeong( Cha Sung Hoon’s Mother ) . Hwang Bo-ra( Journalist Hwang Bo Ra ) . Kim Hyun-sook( Yeo Eui Ju ) . Melina Demir( Business Woman ) . Bae Woo-Hee( Koh Yu Ra ) . Kim Won-shik( Mr. Park )

Language Korean.

Producers Hyunwoo Thomas Kim.

Production Kross Pictures.

 

Number of Seasons 1

Number of Episodes 12

Status OnGoing (2022–)
